{"tid":612732,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"天宮一號將墜落中國？ 中媒稱：不會對地面造成危害","createTime":"2018-04-01T05:53:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-01T08:43:44.000Z","uid":39464,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9f4cba837f0b57ab3a359172a62788e913bfae8a","tid":612732,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T05:53:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2742/d2742378.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2742%2Fd2742378.jpg&h=9ce0bd26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕前年3月失控的中國首座太空站「天宮一號」，其墜落地點及時間引起外界關注。北美防空司令部昨（31日）預測，天宮一號會在台灣時間今上午墜落中國安徽省與河南省的交界處，但歐洲太空總署（ESA）則推測，天宮一號2日才會墜地，但強調日期仍有「變數」。而中國官媒《環球時報》日前曾報導稱，天宮一號不會對地面造成危害。<br />\n<br />\n「中國載人航太工程辦公室」30日公布消息稱，「天宮一號運行在平均高度約189.5公里的軌道上，預計於2018年4月1日加減1天再入大氣層」。《環球時報》則報導，有權威消息指出，「天宮一號」所使用的燃料屬於太空船會使用的燃料，進入大氣層時剩下的少量燃料將會隨結構零件一起燒毀，所以「不會對地面造成危害」。<br />\n<br />\n《環球時報》還說，天宮一號在進入大氣層時，大部分的動能將自動轉為熱能，會使太空船本身燃燒殆盡，所以不會產生有害物質。<br />\n<br />\n但非營利組織「航太公司」（The Aerospace Corporation）則指出，若天宮一號無法在穿越大氣層時整個燒毀，有些含有劇毒且具腐蝕性的化學物質恐散落地上，如此一來會對人體造成傷害。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2383175\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2383175&d=DkDoBY7nHE9Dk66rJNTU4TOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=9a89b3eb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2383175&h=1facf00b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2383175</a>"},{"pid":"194b6f9c5536afc999b3d30e2648c3b005e98106","tid":612732,"uid":104443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T05:54:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">共匪</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da1bcb08310feed1d1b51cac85aa08d99cd4ffca","tid":612732,"uid":26752,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T05:54:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i948.photobucket.com/albums/ad327/ULTRA2020/2012%20JULY/488380_377815688951162_658014377_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi948.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fad327%2FULTRA2020%2F2012%2520JULY%2F488380_377815688951162_658014377_n.jpg&h=3fc11bbf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a26439c50f7cc620a6b75852966a1012921348eb","tid":612732,"uid":56807,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T06:05:43.000Z","msg":"無錯喎，不會對地面危害，只會對地面嘅生命財產危害。"},{"pid":"534cc0db5b46900f2de08facd8fbea2579253c81","tid":612732,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T08:43:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}